data.description: Welcome to your future home! This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home comes with peace of mind, as all the major items have been recently replaced: Furnace & A/C (2021), water heater (2023), carpet & LVP flooring (2023), Roof & Gutters ( back 2023).    The heart of this home features a welcoming fireplace, creating a cozy focal point for gatherings or quiet evenings. Boost your productivity with a dedicated office space featuring French doors, perfect for remote work or personal projects. In the kitchen, discover a chef's paradise with an abundance of storage space, ensuring a clutter-free and organized culinary haven.   The primary ensuite beckons as a private oasis, offering a  soaking tub, separate shower, double sinks, and ample closet space. Upstairs, a versatile loft provides the opportunity to tailor the space to your needs, whether it's an additional bedroom or a creative retreat.  Outside, the lot stretches beyond the fence into the woods, offering unmatched privacy. Step out onto the deck - your perfect spot for morning coffee or evening barbecues with a serene view of nature. This home has been meticulously loved and cared for and is now ready for a new family to create memories!
